::DarkMouse::

She watched as Quickstrike and Stringtra went to greet this flyer 
that had come into there terratory.  She looked at the scanner and 
scanned the bot.  It showed Predacon signature.  But the scanner 
could tell her little else.  She put the signature into the computer 
to store it for later on.  She got up and walked to the entrance and 
looked at the bot hanging upside down in the tree looking at them.
